            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ESatan%20may%20try%20to%20delay%2C%20hinder%2C%20sift%2C%20oppose%2C%20and%20confuse%2C%20but%20the%20moment%20of%20your%20breakthrough%20must%20come.%20Although%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20clock%20move%20almost%20imperceptibly%2C%20the%20moment%20inevitably%20arrives%20when%20the%20clock%20strikes%20the%20hour.%20The%20poet%20Friedrich%20von%20Logau%20expressed%20it%20this%20way%3A%20%22Though%20the%20mills%20of%20God%20grind%20slowly%2C%20yet%20they%20grind%20exceeding%20small%3B%20though%20with%20patience%20He%20stands%20waiting%2C%20with%20exactness%20grinds%20He%20all.%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJesus'%20thirty-three%20years%20of%20preparation%20and%20ministry%20culminated%20in%20the%20glory%20of%20His%20death%20and%20resurrection.%20In%20that%20moment%2C%20the%20prince%20of%20this%20world%20was%20cast%20out%20(John%2012%3A31).%20David%20also%20experienced%20tremendous%20pressure%20in%20his%20years%20of%20preparation%2C%20but%20suddenly%20his%20hour%20came%2C%20Saul%20died%20unexpectedly%2C%20and%20the%20path%20to%20the%20throne%20was%20opened%20(2%20Samuel%202%3A4).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThis%20is%20the%20payoff%20of%20years%20of%20faithful%20service%20to%20a%20vision%3A%20one%20day%20the%20hour%20will%20come.%20Never%20try%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20your%20time%2C%20for%20God%20knows%20when%20the%20circumstances%20are%20ripe%20and%20you%20have%20been%20thoroughly%20prepared.%20All%20your%20trials%20and%20difficulties%20are%20only%20the%20stepping-stones%20to%20your%20glorious%20destiny%3A%20to%20reign%20forever%20with%20Jesus%20Christ!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
