            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Samuel%201%3A1-2%3A11%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Samuel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDavid%20Learns%20of%20Saul%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Death%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20the%20death%20of%20Saul%2C%20David%20returned%20from%20his%20victory%20over%20the%20Amalekites%20and%20spent%20two%20days%20in%20Ziklag.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20the%20third%20day%20a%20man%20arrived%20from%20Saul%26%23x2019%3Bs%20army%20camp.%20He%20had%20torn%20his%20clothes%20and%20put%20dirt%20on%20his%20head%20to%20show%20that%20he%20was%20in%20mourning.%20He%20fell%20to%20the%20ground%20before%20David%20in%20deep%20respect.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhere%20have%20you%20come%20from%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20David%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20escaped%20from%20the%20Israelite%20camp%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20man%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20happened%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20David%20demanded.%20%26%23x201C%3BTell%20me%20how%20the%20battle%20went.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EThe%20man%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BOur%20entire%20army%20fled%20from%20the%20battle.%20Many%20of%20the%20men%20are%20dead%2C%20and%20Saul%20and%20his%20son%20Jonathan%20are%20also%20dead.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BHow%20do%20you%20know%20Saul%20and%20Jonathan%20are%20dead%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20David%20demanded%20of%20the%20young%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20man%20answered%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20happened%20to%20be%20on%20Mount%20Gilboa%2C%20and%20there%20was%20Saul%20leaning%20on%20his%20spear%20with%20the%20enemy%20chariots%20and%20charioteers%20closing%20in%20on%20him.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20he%20turned%20and%20saw%20me%2C%20he%20cried%20out%20for%20me%20to%20come%20to%20him.%20%26%23x2018%3BHow%20can%20I%20help%3F%26%23x2019%3B%20I%20asked%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BHe%20responded%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BWho%20are%20you%3F%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BI%20am%20an%20Amalekite%2C%26%23x2019%3B%20I%20told%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20he%20begged%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BCome%20over%20here%20and%20put%20me%20out%20of%20my%20misery%2C%20for%20I%20am%20in%20terrible%20pain%20and%20want%20to%20die.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_10%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSo%20I%20killed%20him%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20Amalekite%20told%20David%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bfor%20I%20knew%20he%20couldn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20live.%20Then%20I%20took%20his%20crown%20and%20his%20armband%2C%20and%20I%20have%20brought%20them%20here%20to%20you%2C%20my%20lord.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_11%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20and%20his%20men%20tore%20their%20clothes%20in%20sorrow%20when%20they%20heard%20the%20news.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_12%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20mourned%20and%20wept%20and%20fasted%20all%20day%20for%20Saul%20and%20his%20son%20Jonathan%2C%20and%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20army%20and%20the%20nation%20of%20Israel%2C%20because%20they%20had%20died%20by%20the%20sword%20that%20day.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_13%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20said%20to%20the%20young%20man%20who%20had%20brought%20the%20news%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhere%20are%20you%20from%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EAnd%20he%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20a%20foreigner%2C%20an%20Amalekite%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20your%20land.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_1_14%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%